                                                                                                                                Messaging

                                                                                                                                Banner

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                A banner is a contextual message used to communicate a state that is specific to a page or feature. Banners usually remain until dismissed by the user or if the state that caused the banner is resolved.

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                Single line
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Just a heads up."

                                                                                                                                Label: [Message label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Static text


                                                                                                                                With action
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: "You can now customize groups"

                                                                                                                                Label: [Message label]

                                                                                                                                Role: Static text


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: "Dismiss, Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: Dismiss

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                Notes: Allow consumers to voice the image asset or ignore it. Most of the time the icon is redundant to the message text.

                                                                                                                                TalkBack

                                                                                                                                Single line
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Just a heads up."

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: [Message label]

                                                                                                                                Role: TextView

                                                                                                                                With action
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: "You can now customize groups."

                                                                                                                                Label: [Message label]

                                                                                                                                Role: Static text


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: "Dismiss, Button."

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Dismiss

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to activate


                                                                                                                                Notes: Allow consumers to voice the image asset or ignore it. Most of the time the icon is redundant to the message text.
